languages.text: "Я помню то, что мне дозволено. Завет Паутины. Молитвы Неумирающему. Названия ядов и дурманов. Имя, данное Висирем. Тебя... я не помню. Не знаю".

traits.locale_text: "Я помню то, что мне дозволено помнить. Заветы Анн'шини. Молитвы Неумирающему. Названия ядов и дурманов. Имя, данное Висирем. Тебя... я не помню. Тебя я не знаю".

languages.text: "I remember what I am permitted to remember. The Tenets of the Web. Prayers to the Undying One. The names of poisons and intoxicants. The name the Vizsier gave me. But you... No. I do not remember you. I do not know you."
languages.original_text: "Я помню то, что мне дозволено. Завет Паутины. Молитвы Неумирающему. Названия ядов и дурманов. Имя, данное Висирем. Тебя... я не помню. Не знаю".

languages.text: « Je me souviens de ce qu'il m'est permis de conserver dans ma mémoire. Les Préceptes de la Toile. Les prières à l'Immortel. Les noms des poisons et des drogues. Le nom que m'a donné le vizir. Mais vous... Non, je ne garde aucun souvenir de vous. Je ne vous connais pas. »

languages.text: «Recuerdo lo que se me permite recordar. La Doctrina de la Red. Las plegarias al Inmortal. Los nombres de los venenos y productos tóxicos. El nombre que me dio el Visir. Pero a vosotros... No. A vosotros ni os recuerdo ni os conozco».
languages.original_text: "I remember what I am permitted to remember. The Tenets of the Web. Prayers to the Undying One. The names of poisons and intoxicants. The name the Vizsier gave me. But you... No. I do not remember you. I do not know you."

languages.text: 「我は覚えることを許可されたものだけを記憶します。ウェブの信条。不死の者への祈り。毒と中毒物質の名前。ヴィジールが私にくれた名前。だけどあなたは…ダメ。覚えていません。あなたのことは知らない」
languages.original_text: "I remember what I am permitted to remember. The Tenets of the Web. Prayers to the Undying One. The names of poisons and intoxicants. The name the Vizsier gave me. But you... No. I do not remember you. I do not know you."

languages.text: “我只能记起他们允许我铭记的一切——织血罗网的教义、献给不死之神的祈祷、各种毒药与麻醉剂的名称、还有宿老赐予我的名字，可你……不，我不记得你。我不认识你。”
languages.original_text: "I remember what I am permitted to remember. The Tenets of the Web. Prayers to the Undying One. The names of poisons and intoxicants. The name the Vizsier gave me. But you... No. I do not remember you. I do not know you."

languages.text: "Ich erinnere mich an das, was mir gestattet ist. Die Grundsätze des Netzes. Gebete an den Todlosen. Die Namen von Giften und Toxinen. Den Namen, den der Wesir mir gegeben hat. Ihr aber ... Nein. An Euch erinnere ich mich nicht. Ich kenne Euch nicht."
languages.original_text: "I remember what I am permitted to remember. The Tenets of the Web. Prayers to the Undying One. The names of poisons and intoxicants. The name the Vizsier gave me. But you... No. I do not remember you. I do not know you."

languages.text: "Hatırlamama müsaade edildiği kadarını hatırlarım. Ağ'ın İlkeleri, Ölmeyen'e edilen dualar, zehirlerin ve uyarıcı maddelerin isimleri, Vezir'in bana verdiği isim ama sen... Hayır, seni hatırlamıyorum. Seni tanımıyorum."
languages.original_text: "I remember what I am permitted to remember. The Tenets of the Web. Prayers to the Undying One. The names of poisons and intoxicants. The name the Vizsier gave me. But you... No. I do not remember you. I do not know you."
